00:38:44.740 --> 00:38:47.620
They're now very,
very good friends,

00:38:47.620 --> 00:38:49.270
and Darrell is
doing great as well.

00:38:52.380 --> 00:38:54.440
Anybody can change.

00:38:54.440 --> 00:38:56.780
What I'm trying to
say is that it's

00:38:56.780 --> 00:39:01.670
the compassion and the empathy
that we give to those people

00:39:01.670 --> 00:39:04.220
that we despise, that
we hate what they say,

00:39:04.220 --> 00:39:06.920
that changes them.

00:39:06.920 --> 00:39:09.085
Here's another example.

00:39:09.085 --> 00:39:11.100
I don't know if you know
who Richard Spencer.

00:39:11.100 --> 00:39:14.010
Is I'm sure you've
heard his name recently.

00:39:14.010 --> 00:39:16.530
But I was giving a talk last
week in Whitefish, Montana,

00:39:16.530 --> 00:39:21.050
in his hometown, and I sent him
a direct message on Twitter.

00:39:21.050 --> 00:39:22.970
And I said, hey,
I'm in your town.

00:39:22.970 --> 00:39:25.000
Let's grab a coffee.

00:39:25.000 --> 00:39:27.850
And he happened to come
to my talk that night.

00:39:27.850 --> 00:39:32.680
We spoke for two hours
afterwards, and we just talked.

00:39:32.680 --> 00:39:35.200
We didn't battle ideologically.

00:39:35.200 --> 00:39:38.170
I listened, and I listened
for those potholes.

00:39:38.170 --> 00:39:41.260
And of course, I didn't
change Richard Spencer.

00:39:41.260 --> 00:39:42.910
He still hates people.

00:39:42.910 --> 00:39:46.490
He's still pushing
this alt-right agenda.

00:39:46.490 --> 00:39:49.760
But I heard things
that will develop

00:39:49.760 --> 00:39:52.130
into something else over time.

00:39:52.130 --> 00:39:55.940
I heard things about those
voids, those potholes

00:39:55.940 --> 00:39:59.050
in his life, and we've
agreed to meet again.

00:39:59.050 --> 00:40:01.330
And I think a seed
has been planted.

00:40:01.330 --> 00:40:05.470
At least, it's a good sign
that he gave the peace sign.

00:40:05.470 --> 00:40:07.690
But I'm going to
continue talking to him.

00:40:07.690 --> 00:40:09.326
While other people
want to punch him,

00:40:09.326 --> 00:40:11.950
I can tell you that, when I was
18 years old, if somebody would

00:40:11.950 --> 00:40:13.450
have punched me
because of my beliefs,

00:40:13.450 --> 00:40:15.910
I probably would have come back
with something a little bit

00:40:15.910 --> 00:40:17.590
more than a punch.

00:40:17.590 --> 00:40:19.180
That doesn't change anybody.

00:40:19.180 --> 00:40:21.430
I know our initial
reaction is to want

00:40:21.430 --> 00:40:24.340
to eliminate and get rid of
the people who are dissenting

00:40:24.340 --> 00:40:26.009
or say things that
we don't like,

00:40:26.009 --> 00:40:27.550
and I'm here to tell
you that we need

00:40:27.550 --> 00:40:29.560
to listen to them
despite how it makes

00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:31.810
us feel because we
need to establish

00:40:31.810 --> 00:40:34.030
that human connection again.

00:40:34.030 --> 00:40:36.250
That's what helped
me change, and that's

00:40:36.250 --> 00:40:39.370
what I believe will help
change people who are still

00:40:39.370 --> 00:40:40.750
stuck in this movement.

00:40:40.750 --> 00:40:43.120
I have a challenge for
you before we open it up

00:40:43.120 --> 00:40:44.810
for questions.

00:40:44.810 --> 00:40:47.470
I want you to leave
today, and when you leave,

00:40:47.470 --> 00:40:49.020
I want you to do something.

00:40:49.020 --> 00:40:52.220
And that's find
somebody who you think

00:40:52.220 --> 00:40:56.890
doesn't deserve a kind word, and
I want you to give it to them--

00:40:56.890 --> 00:40:58.480
or a kind action.

00:40:58.480 --> 00:41:02.840
Show them compassion,
and see what happens.

00:41:02.840 --> 00:41:07.330
See how you change, and
see how it changes them.

00:41:07.330 --> 00:41:10.140
So I want you to go out there,
and my motto is kind of similar

00:41:10.140 --> 00:41:11.430
to Google's-- the do no evil.

00:41:11.430 --> 00:41:14.400
Mine is make good happen.

00:41:14.400 --> 00:41:16.500
So I want you to go out
there, and I would love

00:41:16.500 --> 00:41:19.417
for you to make good happen.

00:41:19.417 --> 00:41:20.250
Thank you very much.

