all the credit

00:44:40.700 --> 00:44:42.740
for getting yourself
out of where you were.

00:44:42.740 --> 00:44:45.430
But I would imagine there
was someone that helped you.

00:44:45.430 --> 00:44:45.580
CHRISTIAN PICCIOLINI:
A lot of people.

00:44:45.580 --> 00:44:46.600
AUDIENCE: And you didn't
