00:54:58.212 --> 00:54:59.920
different food instead
of chicken nuggets

00:54:59.920 --> 00:55:01.753
and grilled cheese
sandwiches because maybe,

00:55:01.753 --> 00:55:03.490
if they're not afraid
of diverse foods,

00:55:03.490 --> 00:55:07.150
they won't grow up to be
afraid of diverse people.

00:55:07.150 --> 00:55:11.350
I think fathers are so,
so important to young men

00:55:11.350 --> 00:55:14.929
because what I'm seeing is that
so many of these young men that

00:55:14.929 --> 00:55:17.470
are joining these movements are
doing that because they don't

00:55:17.470 --> 00:55:19.660
have a connection
to their father,

00:55:19.660 --> 00:55:24.130
because they're trying to be
something for their father.

00:55:24.130 --> 00:55:26.150
There are a lot of
studies about masculinity

00:55:26.150 --> 00:55:29.527
and the extremist movements
that make a lot, a lot of sense.

00:55:29.527 --> 00:55:31.110
So there are lots
of things we can do.

00:55:31.110 --> 00:55:35.770
We can do something
kind in a small way

00:55:35.770 --> 00:55:37.750
that, if everybody just
does that extra kind

00:55:37.750 --> 00:55:40.480
thing in their life, well,
that's billions of kind things

00:55:40.480 --> 00:55:43.390
that happen every day
that are extra, right?

00:55:43.390 --> 00:55:44.080
Hold the door.

00:55:44.080 --> 00:55:44.980
Say hi to somebody.

00:55:44.980 --> 00:55:47.050
Instead of looking
at your pixels,

00:55:47.050 --> 00:55:49.570
look at eyes when you're
walking down the street.

00:55:49.570 --> 00:55:51.280
There's so many
things that we can

00:55:51.280 --> 00:55:53.620
do that really don't take a
lot of effort that I think

00:55:53.620 --> 00:55:55.190
would really go a long way.

00:55:55.190 --> 00:55:58.090
But opportunity for young
people is so important.

00:55:58.090 --> 00:56:01.060
Instead of after
school day care,

00:56:01.060 --> 00:56:03.520
maybe we should set up
after school incubators

00:56:03.520 --> 00:56:05.590
for young people as
young as six years old

00:56:05.590 --> 00:56:09.700
to start playing around with
things that may take them

00:56:09.700 --> 00:56:11.853
