00:56:53.020 --> 00:56:57.340
We hardly talked about ideology.

00:56:57.340 --> 00:57:01.240
I asked him about his father.

00:57:01.240 --> 00:57:04.480
I asked him about the kinds
of things that he likes to do,

00:57:04.480 --> 00:57:05.590
and I listened.

00:57:05.590 --> 00:57:07.810
And when he would drift
into that ideological space

00:57:07.810 --> 00:57:10.160
and say something
that was a no-no,

00:57:10.160 --> 00:57:11.920
I would tell them
that was a no-no,

00:57:11.920 --> 00:57:15.260
and I would hold him
accountable for that by saying,

00:57:15.260 --> 00:57:18.030
that's not something
that I believe in,

00:57:18.030 --> 00:57:21.020
and I would appreciate it
if you didn't say that.

00:57:21.020 --> 00:57:25.935
And you'd see kind of the
way he would talk shift,

00:57:25.935 --> 00:57:27.560
and he would move on
to something else.

00:57:27.560 --> 00:57:30.370
And he'd started to
go talk about how

00:57:30.370 --> 00:57:33.940
he wanted to be a theater major,
and when we were walking out,

00:57:33.940 --> 00:57:35.930
somebody had come up
to us and said, hey,

00:57:35.930 --> 00:57:37.450
can I tell you how weird
it is that you guys are

00:57:37.450 --> 00:57:39.366
both standing here, and
right next door, we're

00:57:39.366 --> 00:57:43.060
doing a rehearsal for a
performance of Cabaret?

00:57:43.060 --> 00:57:44.650
And his face lit
up, and we started

00:57:44.650 --> 00:57:46.441
to talk about theater
and all these things.

00:57:46.441 --> 00:57:48.490
And it's just hold
them accountable

00:57:48.490 --> 00:57:51.800
in a non-confrontational
way, but still

00:57:51.800 --> 00:57:53.040
keep that dialogue open.

00:57:53.040 --> 00:57:57.690
It would be kind of like
talking to your child, right?

00:57:57.690 --> 00:58:02.860
You wouldn't-- well, but you're
not going to go off and scream

00:58:02.860 --> 00:58:05.099
at your kids and be angry
at them and tell them that

00:58:05.099 --> 00:58:07.390
they're stupid and wrong or
whatever because that's not

00:58:07.390 --> 00:58:09.430
the way you would
handle your kids.

00:58:09.430 --> 00:58:13.320
It's almost like we have
to have those kid gloves,

00:58:13.320 --> 00:58:17.400
but at the same time,
like, no, that's not right,

00:58:17.400 --> 00:58:20.184
and then show them what is right
and have that conversation.

00:58:20.184 --> 00:58:22.350
And they may not agree, and
it may take a long time,

00:58:22.350 --> 00:58:23.880
but that's the way we're going
to get through to people.

00:58:23.880 --> 00:58:26.820
I guarantee you, but arguing
